strings.Value: "Does anyone else want tea? It's growing quite chilly this evening!"

"Thank you, Octavia, your tea is magical! I mean — I didn't mean you used magic to make it... Although you might have, of course... I mean you could have, but not necessarily... That is to say... Thank you."
"No thank you. I am quite content with the cold. And the darkness."
"Oh, thank you, Octavia! This reminds me of our classes at the Academy of Arts — some teachers would often make tea for students. And others sometimes even opened a bottle, ha ha!"
